original_title: UFC Fight Night 154: Moicano vs Korean Zombie
overview: UFC Fight Night 154: Moicano vs Korean Zombie was a mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship held on June 22, 2019, at Bon Secours Wellness Arena in Greenville, South Carolina. A featherweight bout between Renato Moicano and former UFC Featherweight Championship challenger Chan Sung Jung served as the event headliner.
title: UFC Fight Night 154: Moicano vs Korean Zombie
